question: Nalika taun 2001, pira persentase saka 'weighted average number of common shares and dilutive potential common shares' kang disebabake dening 'weighted average partnership units outstanding'?
Yen 'basic net income' ing taun 2002 mundhak 20%, pira rata-rata basic net income anyar ing telung taun kuwi?
Ndelok data kuwi, ana gayutan sing katon antarane 'weighted average number of common shares outstanding' lan 'basic net income available for common shares'?
answer: Katon ana gayutan sing kosok baline antarane rong metrik iki. Nalika jumlah rata-rata saham biasa sing wis metu mundhak ajeg saka taun 2000 nganti 2002, bathi bersih dhasar munggah mudhun, nganti puncake ing taun 2001 sadurunge mudhun menyang titik paling ngisor ing taun 2002, yaiku taun kanthi jumlah saham paling dhuwur. Iki nuduhake yen nalika saham mundhak, bathi ora mesthi nututi, lan nyatane, jumlah saham paling dhuwur cocog karo bathi paling ngisor.
